        {
            "title": "川普促盟友處理霍爾木茲海峽問題 伊朗重申願意結束戰爭",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Institute for the Study of War and AEI’s Critical Threats Project as of March 31 morning Middle East time, Bloomberg News reporting\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"811\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UhYUPRso._.djlE_owizcw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgxMQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e3a5065a4c1be310ef2ca304da58d942\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Institute for the Study of War and AEI’s Critical Threats Project as of March 31 morning Middle East time, Bloomberg News reporting</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統唐納德·川普呼籲其他國家奪取對霍爾木茲海峽的控制，在伊朗繼續在波斯灣發動飛彈攻擊之際，他對這場已持續一個月的戰爭仍未解決表達不滿。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普周二在社交媒體發文稱，因為霍爾木茲海峽陷入癱瘓而無法獲得能源供應的國家應該「去海峽直接拿」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「你們得開始學會為自己而戰，美國不會再幫你們了，」川普表示。這被解讀為美國有意從衝突中抽身的最新信號。「自己去弄你們的石油吧！」他還說。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"觀看：伊朗總統馬蘇德·佩澤希齊揚Source: Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/esNHljPflfzjKoco6E1MIA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c1e6011c0f02e55b1366140a0b0edbb2\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">觀看：伊朗總統馬蘇德·佩澤希齊揚Source: Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在市場押注美伊雙方可能尋求結束戰爭之際，股市上漲、油價下跌。WTI原油約為每桶101美元，旅遊類股上漲，標普500能源指數轉跌，回吐一度達1.4%的漲幅。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-563dd633-3bef-367b-a343-1593f4f7a3b8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗國家通訊社報導稱，伊朗總統馬蘇德·佩澤希齊揚在電話中告訴歐洲理事會主席安東尼奧·科斯塔，伊朗「有結束這場戰爭的必要意願」，但前提是滿足若干條件，「尤其是獲得防止侵略再次發生的必要保障」。目前尚不清楚這一表態是否意味著德黑蘭立場發生變化。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：伊朗結束與美國和以色列戰爭的五大條件</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另據卡達半島電視台報導，伊朗外交部長阿巴斯·阿拉格齊在接受採訪時表示，伊朗與美國之間正在進行的是直接或通過「朋友」進行的信息交換，而不是「談判」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，德黑蘭繼續對以色列及波斯灣周邊國家發動打擊，擊中了杜拜外海一艘滿載的科威特油輪。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美以聯盟也持續打擊伊朗，結束衝突的外交努力尚未出現突破跡象。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國國防部長皮特·海格塞斯表示，與伊朗的談判勢頭「正在增強」，美軍將繼續施壓以迫使德黑蘭達成協議。他還稱伊朗「已發生政權更迭」，但未說明美方的談判對象。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國和巴基斯坦提出了旨在恢復中東和平的五點倡議，首先是立即停火止戰。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"811\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GMAR1LZAshzvj4Gh1Y.Pfg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgxMQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ec388d242d81068556d932bede9536e8\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普還在社交媒體上批評英國和法國，抱怨傳統盟友在衝突中支持不足。北約成員基本避免捲入衝突，據知情人士稱，西班牙關閉領空禁止美國打擊伊朗的飛機通行，義大利也拒絕一架美軍飛機降落在西西裡島的基地。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周二，全美平均汽油價格自2022年8月以來首次突破每加侖4美元，這可能在中期選舉臨近之際進一步加大川普解決危機的壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Calls on Allies to Seize Hormuz as Frustration Mounts (3)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Iran, US Exchanging Messages, No Talks: Araghchi to AlJazeera</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Omar Tamo、Golnar Motevalli、Dan Williams、Kateryna Kadabashy.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(新增伊朗總統、伊朗外長講話)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%86%8D%E5%BA%A6%E5%90%91%E7%9B%9F%E5%8F%8B%E7%99%BC%E9%9B%A3-%E5%96%8A%E8%A9%B1%E7%BC%BA%E6%B2%B9%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%8E%BB%E9%9C%8D%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%A8%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E8%87%AA%E5%8F%96-162834235.html",
